{"tid":2499141,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解少左咁多龍門食評po?","createTime":"2021-04-21T15:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T02:26:27.000Z","uid":396616,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d26dcee68a82688a36512cd6aaf2075ab0e5e4b","tid":2499141,"uid":396616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"你地其實係咪已經冇左個良心？<br />\n日日抹黑龍門<br />\n係咁講精液蛋 半生熟中式牛柳<br />\n依件野唔熟都食得囉<br />\n食左都唔會死啦<br />\n咁都驚一餐<br />\n對唔對得住搵命搏嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n又話佢啲野食對唔住個價錢<br />\n大佬呀黃店唔洗賺錢咩<br />\n乾柴叉燒咪又係叉燒<br />\n講到食屎咁唔請你真係食過屎咩<br />\n張老闆日日去搵游水魚比手足食<br />\n個人工都喺度啦<br />\n<br />\n仲要話人地啲野難食<br />\n你地到底記唔記得個初心係咩<br />\n我地係要食良心而唔係食美食<br />\n乜野好食是良知係得班藍絲先會講<br />\n要記住龍門執等於場運動輸<br />\n張老闆唔係condom"},{"pid":"818e5ef8d4a0b8bedf302fce6905655b65d3c76c","tid":2499141,"uid":396616,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"@蝻亞仔<br />\n@孩子飛飛<br />\n@支那人就是國恥<br />\n@牧養犬<br />\n@鬼二二"},{"pid":"0ef9e15675b4bc70194ef056a7127b72dcdd7c0c","tid":2499141,"uid":1823,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"冇錢請打手咪少左post囉"},{"pid":"89e26ae42a671cd76402f0aba32b3b5ab5c9d7ee","tid":2499141,"uid":140583,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"其實已經無人屌好耐 係得啲人係度屌啲人屌<br />\n低級分化post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea18bf70af5e297b969b44c6e715af0a8aa2e6f","tid":2499141,"uid":96303,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ef9e15675b4bc70194ef056a7127b72dcdd7c0c","tid":2499141,"uid":1823,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"冇錢請打手咪少左post囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"可能係庇護工場手足<br />\n唔係打手黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829e2e8e5c63943dc4d8619fd3e2a83947ea94fd","tid":2499141,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:5